<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>٤٠ -<span class="c5"> ١٢٠:</span> شاة.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>١٢١ -<span class="c5"> ٢٠٠:</span> شاتان.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>٢٠١ -<span class="c5"> ٣٩٩:</span> ثلاث شياه.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>ثم في كل <span class="c2">(١٠٠)</span> شاة،<span class="c5"> فمثلاً:</span> ٤٠٠ - ٤٩٩ أربع شياه، ٥٠٠ - ٥٩٩ خمس شياه.<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>